The Benue South Senator, Comrade Abba Moro has picked the Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, Senatorial ticket. Abba Moro retained his ticket as the party’s Senatorial flag bearer in the 2023 general elections, after defeating his fellow aspirants during PDP primary election held in Otukpo on Tuesday. The incumbent Senator garnered 179 votes ahead of Hassan Anthony Saleh, Joe Ojobo and Bright Ogaji. See results of the primary elections below… Abba Moro – 179 Hassan Anthony Saleh – 72 Joe Ojobo – 53 Bright Ogaji – 3.